 <title>SCALE 10x - 2012 Southern California Linux Expo - ScaleU</title>
 <link>https://www.socallinuxexpo.org/taxonomy/term/15</link>
 <description>The SCALE University training program continues for SCALE 10x. The classes give a more intense and personal learning experience than a 45-minute seminar.
We are offering half-day classes for system administrators of all skill and experience levels. The SCALE University Pass  ($300) includes a full day of training (two classes of your choice) and full access to all three days of SCALE. To register, select the &quot; Full Access Pass&quot; and then the &quot;SCALE University Pass&quot; which will include a $60 discount on your total charge.
The SCALE University classes will be held on Friday, Janury 20th, 2012. 
</description>
